text: László Gellér (born 5 August 1944) is a Hungarian ski jumper. He competed at the 1964 Winter Olympics and the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Hungary Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Tótkomlós
